origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'FinanceAPI.get_market_liquidity', 'description': 'This function provides an analysis of market liquidity based on the market type, time frame, and date range.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'marketType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial market, e.g., stocks, bonds, commodities.'}, {'name': 'timeFrame', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time frame for the analysis, e.g., daily, weekly, monthly.'}, {'name': 'startDate', 'type': 'DATE', 'description': 'The start date of the analysis.'}, {'name': 'endDate', 'type': 'DATE', 'description': 'The end date of the analysis.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'liquidityAnalysis', 'description': 'The analysis of market liquidity including volume, velocity, and factors influencing liquidity.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 FinanceAPI.get_market_liquidity, 它的参数输入如下: 'marketType'是'stocks', 'timeFrame'是'monthly', 'startDate'是'2023-01-01', 'endDate'是'2023-12-31'.
